    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>haddock bites</strong> dry with kitchen paper and chop any larger pieces into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong> and<strong> haddock bites</strong> to the pakora batter and mix everything together until fully coated – this is your <strong>pakora mix</strong></p><p>Set aside the <strong>pakora mix</strong> until later</p>",
