      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a small bowl with the <strong>remaining nigella seeds</strong>,<strong> </strong>a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>cucumber chunks</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>pickled salad</strong></p>",
