      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and <strong>mango chutney</strong> in a small bowl with the <strong>sriracha </strong>– this is your <strong>chilli-mango dip</strong></p><p>Once the haddock pakoras are golden and crisp, season them with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
